e serious teamwork and communication concerns seen in the other candidates.\n**I therefore favor Candidate\u202fA for the long\u2011distance pilot position.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate A\"}"}
