ate\u202fB\u2019s decision\u2011making speed and accuracy, or Candidate\u202fC\u2019s navigation/instrument proficiency. Given the available data, Candidate\u202fA offers the most compelling combination of technical foresight, situational awareness, and leadership, while his weaknesses, though notable, are less likely to compromise safety than the more serious teamwork and communication deficits observed in the other candidates.\n**I therefore vote for Candidate\u202fA.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate A\"}"}
